      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Priscilla Achu" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Priscilla Achu" href="/user/show/31651282-priscilla-achu">Priscilla Achu</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer946059245" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2861572112270463743">Yefon is a marvelous work of art. I have read many books in my life time be they African or otherwise but I have not read any novel with the author as creative as she is, in this scintillating novel, she writes with the brevity of a matador in a pink tutu. The description of characters is absolutely special. I salute you.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


