<span id="freeTextContainer11943291559547057418">About Author Sahndra Fon Dufe: Cameroonian-born author, actress, humanitarian and business mogul Sahndra Fon Dufe is the young CEO of African Pictures International, and co-founder of Gifted Minds Africa Foundation. She works at exposing the history, culture, and truth about Africa, women and the spirit within. The remarkable actress has been featured in numerous feature films, and commercials, an</span>
  <span id="freeText11943291559547057418" style="display:none">About Author Sahndra Fon Dufe: Cameroonian-born author, actress, humanitarian and business mogul Sahndra Fon Dufe is the young CEO of African Pictures International, and co-founder of Gifted Minds Africa Foundation. She works at exposing the history, culture, and truth about Africa, women and the spirit within. The remarkable actress has been featured in numerous feature films, and commercials, and presently lives in Los Angeles with her hunk of a man, a closet full of shoes and too many vintage clothes. Sahndra spends her spare time perfecting her craft and soul-searching, on a journey to regain wholeness and cure the spirit. She also hunts for Egyptian artifacts, pieces which have captivated her imagination since childhood. To read her full biography visit her official website at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.sahndrafondufe/bio">http://www.sahndrafondufe/bio</a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sahndra_Fon_Dufe">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sahndra_...</a>, and <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm4677827">http://www.imdb.com/name/nm4677827</a> You can follow Author Sahndra Fon Dufe on Twitter at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.twitter.com/sahndrafondufe">www.twitter.com/sahndrafondufe</a> and Like her Facebook at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.facebook.com/sahndrafondufeofficial">www.facebook.com/sahndrafondufeofficial</a></span>
